{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"acae60d077","title":"羞於见人的几篇日记","origin":"《关于“野草”、“蜜蜂”社反动小集团的材料》，中共中央民族学院整风办公室编，1957年12月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ff9089c60a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":30,"articleId":"acae60d077"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"6dd61a6c39","name":"中央民族学院"},{"id":"ed639f1bc5","name":"王佐良"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"818f5cf62c","type":"title","text":"羞于见人的几篇日记","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"2280b52fd9","type":"authors","text":"中央民族学院王成良","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"2ad97abe82","type":"subtitle","text":"（王成良：中央民族学院语文系一年级藏语班学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"d1f182d9b8","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"a79befefab","type":"paragraph","text":"我已预感到自己在辩论会上将扮演怎样的丑角，……所以……","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"cbbc787e6d","type":"paragraph","text":"我写给梦侠一个小条，台头上在梦侠二字后边破天荒的加上了个甜蜜而亲切的称呼：“大姐”……。我颇想藉此唤醒她女性的慈柔和怜悯，以便让我避过这次“会”，但是……见鬼去吧！","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"a9799566eb","type":"paragraph","text":"萧洛霍夫说的对：“生活总是以自己的不成文法支配着人类！”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"fa52df7410","type":"paragraph","text":"我只好出席了。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"34f4b298d1","type":"paragraph","text":"会场上，全系同学济济一堂。我被三番五次，文质彬彬的邀请，请在了会场中间坐下。众目睽睽的射向我，我……，我感到同学们所坐椅子的脚都压在我的头上，我颇感支持不住这样沉重的负荷……。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"7b4a95aa55","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"aa356a82bf","type":"paragraph","text":"争辨(辩)愈来愈加激烈了……。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"d78c7b203e","type":"paragraph","text":"李德君同学发言。他那激恕的情绪，象一盆熊熊在燃的火；他喊出的每字、每句，都那么铿锵有力，象飞爆的火花一样，向会场四散迸射。会场的空气，象一锅油一样，紧张而滑腻。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"2347170f97","type":"paragraph","text":"李德君同学脸也红了。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"8c149c6a18","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"332dfc227f","type":"paragraph","text":"火越燃越旺……","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"8c9820ea83","type":"paragraph","text":"火花越迸越多……","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"feb0e91a72","type":"paragraph","text":"油热了……油烫了……终于油达到了沸点，沸腾起来了，哗哗哗一片掌声……，我象突然被扔进了油锅里一样的狼狈……痛苦……难堪……","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"ec1a396b2d","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"15b7eebc73","type":"paragraph","text":"李德君的激昂陈词之后……，专修科一位戴眼镜的同学发言……我惊悉李德君同学式的发言，竟不独有隅(偶)。紧接着刘仁培声音更大……，鼎足而三了……，三三见九了……，九九八十一了……，来吧！一切右派的阴谋家，从这些发言中，体验一下党在群众中盘石般的威信和力量吧！","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"aaf46a8929","type":"subtitle","text":"五","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"e9889ba67f","type":"paragraph","text":"为了使自己脑袋不至炸开，我蹓在会场外边徘徊。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"a101c27a5f","type":"paragraph","text":"当我一在会场门口露头，成千双眼光的火力点，都集中向我鼻尖上。其中有愤慨的……，有愠怒的……，有嘲弄的……，我即刻感到象往鼻孔里灌进一碗酸、甜、苦、辣、咸的调味品一样，尴尬，难呛……。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"ae1e7db3fe","type":"paragraph","text":"忽然，主席站起来：“现在，大家一致要求让王成良到会场里边来……”。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"5724a09199","type":"paragraph","text":"主席是位沉静、严肃的姑娘。所以，假若从李德君发言声中，使人联想到木棍和铁棒的话；那么，主席的声音，只能让人联想到柔软而金光闪亮的丝绳。但是这丝绳，因有“让王成良……”四字在内，就产生了异乎寻常的力量，而象一条长而韧的套索一样，一下准而稳的套在我的脖子上，我身不由己的被拉向会场。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"ce4ee43c28","type":"paragraph","text":"我的脑袋涨大了，……","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"23983b5a23","type":"paragraph","text":"我的腿变长了，……","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"6ff81fe36b","type":"paragraph","text":"我的胳膊和手不知放在何处为宜，下意识的把一根手指头插向了肮脏的鼻孔里……。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"e83aafc359","type":"subtitle","text":"六","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"e221566742","type":"paragraph","text":"会，继续进行……","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"b52f77d87b","type":"paragraph","text":"一个接一个发言，主席手里要求发言的纸条一大把一大把的。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"be49865748","type":"paragraph","text":"我坐在中间，象热锅上的蚂蚁一样，在焦躁和不安中，我模糊的意识到全国打退右派进攻那怒涛般的力量，我继而又清醒的感到：这个会场是这个怒涛的一个浪花，一个典型的浪花……。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"53a491482c","type":"subtitle","text":"七","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"45d711cad0","type":"paragraph","text":"辩论会结束后：我的心……跳的久久不能平静……。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"50f59d1f6a","type":"paragraph","text":"我回到宿舍，焦躁的来回踱了几步，把耳机子戴在了耳朵上，中央第二台，正在广播冼星海的黄河大合唱组歌中的黄河颂一曲，那男声合唱雄浑的胸音，海哟声！配合着管弦乐器和打击乐器，那沉重而粗犷的旋律，立刻把黄河那汹涌澎湃的万顷波涛带进了我的心胸，波涛以它有力的节凑(奏)拍击着我的心胸，我想跳起狂舞！我想放开嗓子大喊！让我的声音风送万里传向世界，祖国！我的祖国！我知道你在怎样波澜壮阔的前进着！！","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"f53a05a620","type":"appellation","text":"(录自“野草”第5期)","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"3fb8814ef1","type":"subtitle","text":"祖国","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"ac04003bb5","type":"subtitle","text":"汪洋(王成良)","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"d811987629","type":"paragraph","text":"祖国","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"1805d79625","type":"paragraph","text":"我是你一个最普通的公民","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"a0c84e31d7","type":"paragraph","text":"象你六亿孩子中的任何一个","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"b2eaa6e5bb","type":"paragraph","text":"我看着你","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"6ffe723f4f","type":"paragraph","text":"不论白天和黑夜","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"8b4ebc4a2c","type":"paragraph","text":"情不自禁的泪水","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"8868f57e49","type":"paragraph","text":"总象不断淙淙淌流的小流","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"1d049ba4dc","type":"paragraph","text":"今天　我流着泪","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"ec34eab025","type":"paragraph","text":"明天　我流着泪","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"3cfe8a5961","type":"paragraph","text":"后天  我的泪将更多的","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"c2ee7b0bef","type":"paragraph","text":"从我那对你永不能无动于衷的脸上流过！","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"35561a5e8c","type":"paragraph","text":"一直到我死去","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"95acd35f82","type":"paragraph","text":"尸体葬入墓穴","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"6d861223bd","type":"paragraph","text":"烂成泥土一撮","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"a08bf56eee","type":"paragraph","text":"但是　我的泪水","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"1112e75878","type":"paragraph","text":"将永不枯竭","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"dd687bd81b","type":"paragraph","text":"它会象两注泉水一样","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"bb86943783","type":"paragraph","text":"涌出地面","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"888de2d8ff","type":"paragraph","text":"流呀  流呀  永流不歇","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"c22446e5a9","type":"paragraph","text":"祖国啊……","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"b898cc50ce","type":"paragraph","text":"我的祖国","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"ff693bfd59","type":"paragraph","text":"你的普通公民的眼泪","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"f0f4099c3d","type":"paragraph","text":"有痛的","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"a8b85842f9","type":"paragraph","text":"有激愤的","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"c9dc2cdb73","type":"paragraph","text":"但更多的","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"c10a28662c","type":"paragraph","text":"而且是：愈来愈更多的","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"06cdd36b9b","type":"paragraph","text":"是：欢乐的","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"},{"id":"906d30f016","type":"paragraph","text":" (录自“野草”第5期)","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077"}],"page":{"id":"99b2798c72","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"acae60d077","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}